{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/blog/i-want-to-write-a-novel","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Hmm, I will go through this questionnaire.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.1560283687943262;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/74c494a50593a03018104edfcba3967d/50383/i-want-to-write-a-novel.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.50306748466258%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ChatGPT4 questionnaire for writing a novel\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/74c494a50593a03018104edfcba3967d/a6d36/i-want-to-write-a-novel.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/74c494a50593a03018104edfcba3967d/222b7/i-want-to-write-a-novel.png 163w,\n/static/74c494a50593a03018104edfcba3967d/ff46a/i-want-to-write-a-novel.png 325w,\n/static/74c494a50593a03018104edfcba3967d/a6d36/i-want-to-write-a-novel.png 650w,\n/static/74c494a50593a03018104edfcba3967d/50383/i-want-to-write-a-novel.png 740w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"1-genre\" style=\"position:relative;\">1. Genre<a href=\"#1-genre\" aria-label=\"1 genre permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>One of my favorite authors is Howard Phillips Lovecraft. He writes horror, but I will go with mystery because I want my characters to keep their sanity (all Lovecraft's protagonists end up in madhouse</p>\n<p>Not that I'm good at writing, but maybe in the future I will find this plan and confirm if I still want to write such a story</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-target-audience\" style=\"position:relative;\">2. Target audience<a href=\"#2-target-audience\" aria-label=\"2 target audience permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>I would write for young adults. That age when you might study at a university and when you are looking for true love. When everyone around you is a braggart liar, and you are trying to find a job that will make this world better</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-primary-theme\" style=\"position:relative;\">3. Primary theme<a href=\"#3-primary-theme\" aria-label=\"3 primary theme permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Primary theme? This is hard. Can I just write? I like the sound of my keyboard. Okay, just kidding.\nMy main message will be YOLO. Don't look back. Live the life that you enjoy.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-plot\" style=\"position:relative;\">4. Plot<a href=\"#4-plot\" aria-label=\"4 plot permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Approximate plot idea.</p>\n<p>Our main protagonist is a guy who studies at the university and falls in love with a girl from his class. But he doesn't tell her about it.</p>\n<p>One day she disappears, and the guy finds the courage to ask around. But unexpectedly, people who knew her began revealing strange facts about her life. Some secret project she was conducting at night. A bit of mystery, a bit of conspiracy...</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-main-characters\" style=\"position:relative;\">5. Main characters<a href=\"#5-main-characters\" aria-label=\"5 main characters permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>So we have a guy and a girl. We need a sidekick. Or it can be an internal monologue as I always do in real life. But if I add the sidekick, then there will be a place for betrayal. What is life without betrayal from your friend?</p>\n<h2 id=\"6-setting\" style=\"position:relative;\">6. Setting<a href=\"#6-setting\" aria-label=\"6 setting permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>The setting for this novel is very mundane: life on campus and work in a laboratory. Present days, but maybe going back to the 60s</p>\n<h2 id=\"7-mood\" style=\"position:relative;\">7. Mood<a href=\"#7-mood\" aria-label=\"7 mood permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>The overall mood will be dark. Like all my life. But some moments are going to be heartwarming like when the main character overcomes challenges, finds a deep connection with another person, and has a moment when he finds a glimmer of hope</p>\n<h2 id=\"8-structure\" style=\"position:relative;\">8. Structure<a href=\"#8-structure\" aria-label=\"8 structure permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>I can only think of a linear narrative. At least the first draft can be written this way. But when Tarantino will start a movie adaptation, he will divide everything into episodes and shuffle anyway.</p>\n<p>t reminds me of beatnik literature. Their narrative is very specific. To achieve it, they split the page into two columns, then write the main plot in one column, and some thoughts and hardly relevant text in another column, then mix it in the final version. Example: Naked Lunch.</p>\n<h2 id=\"9-literary-devices\" style=\"position:relative;\">9. Literary devices<a href=\"#9-literary-devices\" aria-label=\"9 literary devices permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Literary tropes and stylistic elements? Something like this: the whole novel is a big flashback, and the main narrative starts and ends in the last chapter.</p>\n<p>I remember my mom complained about one of Paulo Coelho's books like what is the message in this book. The allegory was too incomprehensible. And her friend said: now think that the main character is a small chicken and you will understand. My mom: no, the book is stupid.</p>\n<p>So I should be careful with literature devices. But I want to use irony - when the opposite of what is expected happens. For example, our guy who thinks he has found his calling in a particular subject ends up discovering a new passion in an unexpected area.</p>\n<h2 id=\"10-working-title\" style=\"position:relative;\">10. Working title<a href=\"#10-working-title\" aria-label=\"10 working title permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>...</p>\n<h2 id=\"also\" style=\"position:relative;\">Also<a href=\"#also\" aria-label=\"also permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Also it can be a plot in a <a href=\"/ideas/romantic-cthulhu\">casual mobile game</a></p>","excerpt":"Hmm, I will go through this questionnaire.  1. Genre One of my favorite authors is Howard Phillips Lovecraft. He writes horror, but I will…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-genre\">1. Genre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-target-audience\">2. Target audience</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-primary-theme\">3. Primary theme</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-plot\">4. Plot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#5-main-characters\">5. Main characters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#6-setting\">6. Setting</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#7-mood\">7. Mood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#8-structure\">8. Structure</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#9-literary-devices\">9. Literary devices</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#10-working-title\">10. Working title</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#also\">Also</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"socialcard":"gatsby-plugin-social-card/61662e63-0562-5295-9fa0-b1ff615cb0ee.jpg"},"frontmatter":{"date":"April 27, 2023","published":"April 27, 2023","lastModified":"April 27, 2023","t